{"tid":1713421,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"見到有人用弓箭 真心覺得危險同埋唔好再咁做","createTime":"2019-11-12T17:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T10:50:03.000Z","uid":82312,"like":140,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"a247c9c19dd3bcc8b11285cc665d5b76bd96fe07","tid":1713421,"uid":82312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:26:36.000Z","msg":"連登真係好多暴徒<br />\n痴線 我呼籲大家真係唔好再咁做<br />\n會死人 一陣D學生唔識野<br />\n拎條雞泡魚D皮同內臟搽箭頭<br />\n分分鐘變左D毒吹箭咁致命 河豚毒係世界上最毒嘅天然毒素<br />\n好危險 仲要世界上冇解藥<br />\n仲要香港成個海都可以釣到雞泡魚<br />\n真係唔好發生左悲劇先做野<br />\n<br />\n政府應該盡快撈走晒香港海域D雞泡魚<br />\n始終有危險性<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n表達意見其實拉下人鏈同埋寫下信比政府已經好足夠<br />\n暴力始終唔好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f046840c196dcce1893d6538a56548ed326fd6","tid":1713421,"uid":335708,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:32:24.000Z","msg":"千奇五好甘做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe53e29aebf9d8874be2b68ad5d85cc2c3329ad","tid":1713421,"uid":82312,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"98f046840c196dcce1893d6538a56548ed326fd6","tid":1713421,"uid":335708,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:32:24.000Z","msg":"千奇五好甘做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />D紅